      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish with no swirl marks, chips, or dings, complemented by pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh performance rubber. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero wear, and every electronic feature functions perfectly. This car has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, always garaged, and never driven in inclement weather. The engine bay is spotless, reflecting the mechanical perfection of this low-mileage gem. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a turnkey example of automotive excellence.",
